text: Alireza Rafieipour (, born 3 October 1993) is an Iranian futsal player. He is currently a member of SKN Kebumen in the Indonesia Pro Futsal League. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:People from Behbahan Category:Iranian men's futsal players Category:Futsal defenders Category:Melli Haffari FSC players Category:Iranian expatriate futsal players Category:Iranian expatriate sportspeople in Iraq Category:Iranian expatriate sportspeople in Vietnam Category:Iranian expatriate sportspeople in Indonesia
